en_497929_0	Employees of the Pugoda Textile Factory were awarded compensation after 19 years.
en_497929_1	About 2300 workers were serving in the Government owned Pugoda Factory at the time of its closure.
en_497929_2	The Finance Ministry decided to pay their salary arrears.
en_497929_3	Accordingly the payment of the related compensation took place recently at the auditorium of the Dompe Divisional Secretariat.
en_497929_4	Noteworthy was the participation of officials other than any political representatives.
en_497929_5	The workers expressed their appreciation to the Government for the awarding of compensation to them after several years.
